; melee_heavy.tres — the finisher of the claw combo.
;
; Design intent: the PAYOFF for the cancel. High damage but long recovery (24f = 0.4s) if
; whiffed or not followed up — the punish window that makes mashing punishable. A skilled
; player cancels light->heavy during the combo window and either commits (high damage) or
; cancels the heavy's recovery into a dash (escape). A masher who spams attack gets the
; heavy's full recovery every time.
;
; Small lifesteal reinforces the "predator" fantasy: the combo's end is a feed.
;
[gd_resource type="Resource" script_class="ActionDef" load_steps=2 format=3]

